context.arch.storage
Class Attribute<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>

java.lang.Object
  context.arch.storage.Attribute<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AttributeFunction, AttributeNameValue
public class Attribute<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>
extends java.lang.Object

This class is a container for an attribute name, subAttributes (used for structures - STRUCT) and type. Implements Comparable; for proper operation Attributes must compare by name.
